{"tid":1730442,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［學術討論］[烏克蘭火油桶］唔贊成咁做！","createTime":"2019-11-17T13:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T16:49:37.000Z","uid":66870,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"33baf3c2dee51027ef516ffb6e5dabc89efdad9f","tid":1730442,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNJ8E6V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNJ8E6V.jpg&h=4c0e60aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前見烏克蘭人抗爭有用過呢招！<br />\n可以係油桶度放雜物燃燒 草呀報紙呀<br />\n燒到一定程度 用滾既方式推去敵人果邊<br />\n數量要多 而且要有速度<br />\n對面個陣型就會散！隨時撞到燒到對面癡線！<br />\n真係唔建議香港都咁做 萬一燒到撞到啲popo點算！！<br />\n可以用黎推進同破陣！好擔心啲popo會整親！千祈唔好<br />\n唔知有冇人有相關既片 小弟搵唔返呢種火油桶戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cb08f02db1d916db3f4e2df80b859c525dde98","tid":1730442,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人有片一齊研究？"},{"pid":"81f194343792fe5008951b65086533cce0c5ee72","tid":1730442,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1453651cbba2e7fc264dcb8bf453b18dfbfb0277","tid":1730442,"uid":216710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"邊度搵油桶先得架"},{"pid":"5f600bd955be173f154c1119d46ced937c1c24dc","tid":1730442,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:36:30.000Z","msg":"埋土學生千祈唔好咁做！前線千祈唔好！"},{"pid":"d101e959bf7bd1e39a112a17e106e91e5caa15ec","tid":1730442,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"